title: The Stalled Growth Story With Leverage Anchor
short_thesis: LDOS is a low-growth legacy defense contractor masked as a compounder. Yes, revenue CAGR looks okay (5yr: 6.9%), but the growth is decelerating hard: Q1 2026 only +3.65% YoY after Q4 2025's -3.62%. The 3yr revenue CAGR is 6.1%, essentially flat vs 5yr, signaling mature business with no acceleration. EPS growth (30.9% 3yr CAGR) is entirely accounting-driven buybacks and margin expansion, not organi
